  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>, specialized in transporting cargo. Pre-fitted with upgraded <span class=\"name name-technology\">Deflector Shields</span> and a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cargo Scan Deflector</span>, this hauler craft is ideal for ensuring precious goods - legal or otherwise - stay intact in transit.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，专门用于运输货物。预先安装了升级版<span class=\"name name-technology\">偏导护盾</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">货物扫描偏导器</span>，这艘运输船是确保珍贵货物（不管合法与否）在运输中保持完好的理想选择。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，專門用來運送貨物。預裝了升級版<span class=\"name name-technology\">反射防護罩</span>和一個<span class=\"name name-technology\">貨物掃描反射器</span>，此運輸飛行器十分適合保護珍貴的貨物，不論是否合法，運送過程都能安全無虞。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>皆可。在星球上時，可利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
